sequenceDiagram
    participant App as App / Cache Client
    participant Ring as Consistent Hash Ring
    participant N as Cache Node (shard)
    participant DB as Database

    Note over App,DB: Read-through with miss + write-through update
    App->>Ring: hash(key) -> shard
    Ring-->>App: node = N
    App->>N: GET key
    alt cache hit
        N-->>App: value
    else cache miss
        N-->>App: nil
        App->>App: acquire single-flight lock (per key)
        App->>DB: SELECT value WHERE key=...
        DB-->>App: value
        App->>N: SET key value EX ttl_jittered
        N-->>App: OK
        App->>App: release single-flight lock
        Note over App: concurrent waiters read freshly-set key
    end

    Note over App,DB: Write-through update path
    App->>DB: UPDATE record (source of truth)
    DB-->>App: OK
    App->>N: DEL key (invalidate, do not SET)
    N-->>App: OK
    Note over N: next reader misses -> reloads fresh value
